        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Jehoshaphat the son of Ahilud, the recorder; who was in the same office in the times of David, and now held it under Solomon, 2 Samuel 8:16. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "Jehoshaphat the son of Ahilud, the recorder; who was in the same office in the times of David, and now held it under Solomon, ",
